  <title>Floating point 字面量</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Currency</keyword>
    <keyword>Currency Literal</keyword>
    <keyword>Floating point Literals</keyword>
    <keyword>Literals</keyword>
    <keyword>Numeric Literals</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Floating point 字面量</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">单精度或双精度字面量可用于在代码中存储数值。</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">123.456</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">123.0</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">0.123</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">.123</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">123.456e+7</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">123.456e-7</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">$123.45</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Real 字面量可以有以下后缀之一：</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="4" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;">后缀</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;">描述</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">S 或 s</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">单精度 (REAL4)</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">D 或 d</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">双精度 (REAL8)</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">M 或 m</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">十进制</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">不带后缀的浮点(Floating point)字面量以 REAL8 格式存储，除非指定了<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="opt-vo14">/vo14</link> 编译器选项，在这种情况下，浮点字面量以 FLOAT 格式存储。.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;">前缀</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;">描述</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal">$</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="CURRENCY">Currency</link> 字面量</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
